Two thousand dead.


46
00:03:45.812 --> 00:03:47.854
Whole place is nothing but
pestilential swamp.


47
00:03:48.022 --> 00:03:52.150
Typhus, malaria, cholera, yellow fever.
You name it, they got it.


48
00:03:52.318 --> 00:03:53.777
You see that, Mr. Dietrich?

49
00:03:54.779 --> 00:03:58.824
You are looking at the largest
private air force in the entire world.


50
00:03:58.991 --> 00:04:01.034
What do you think of that, now?

51
00:04:02.453 --> 00:04:03.995
