52
00:04:04.163 --> 00:04:06.581
Start them up!

53
00:05:32.543 --> 00:05:36.379
I saw the rough cut of the new
Tod Browning movie, London After Midnight.


54
00:05:36.547 --> 00:05:38.340
Lon Chaney is incredible.

55
00:05:38.508 --> 00:05:40.842
It's his best performance
in a long time.


56
