58
00:05:45.097 --> 00:05:47.557
Hello, Mr. Mayer.

59
00:05:47.725 --> 00:05:50.727
I don't know if you remember me.
My name's Howard Hughes.


60
00:05:50.895 --> 00:05:53.271
I was wondering
if I could have a moment.


61
00:05:53.439 --> 00:05:56.483
- Oh, Howard Hughes. The airplane picture?
- Exactly.


62
00:05:56.651 --> 00:05:58.985
- I remember.
- Hell's Angels. You heard of it.


63
00:05:59.153 --> 00:06:00.403
- Good.
- Yes.


64
00:06:00.571 --> 00:06:03.365
I was wondering if I could
have a moment of your time.


65
00:06:03.533 --> 00:06:04.824
I need a few cameras.

66
00:06:05.660 --> 00:06:08.662
- Yeah?
- Yeah, two, to be exact.


67
00:06:09.580 --> 00:06:13.625
I bought every camera I could find.
We're shooting our big dogfight sequence.


68
00:06:13.793 --> 00:06:17.212
I need two more. Desperately.
You think MGM could help me out?


69
00:06:17.505 --> 00:06:18.755
With what?

70
00:06:18.923 --> 00:06:21.716
- Cameras.
- Oh, with the actual cam --


71
00:06:21.884 --> 00:06:25.095
We're not usually in the practice
of helping out competition.


72
00:06:25.346 --> 00:06:28.390
- No. No.
- So how many cameras do you have now?


73
00:06:28.558 --> 00:06:29.933
Twenty-four.

74
00:06:32.478 --> 00:06:35.105
You ...?
Wait a minute.


75
00:06:37.358 --> 00:06:39.234
- You have 24 cameras?
- That's right.


76
00:06:39.402 --> 00:06:41.987
- And you need --? You need two more?
- Yeah.


77
00:06:42.154 --> 00:06:45.782
- You don't think you got it with 24?
- No. No, sir.


78
00:06:45.950 --> 00:06:48.577
You know, I think --
I think we've got them all ...


79
00:06:48.744 --> 00:06:51.162
Don't we have them ...?
They're all used, right?


80
00:06:51.330 --> 00:06:53.623
- All 26 of them.
- I only need two, sir.


81
00:06:53.791 --> 00:06:55.667
- Jesus Christ, sonny.
- Howard.


82
00:06:55.835 --> 00:06:58.503
Howard. Let me give you
a little advice, huh?


83
00:06:58.671 --> 00:07:00.755
- Take your oil money --
- Drill bits.


84
00:07:00.923 --> 00:07:04.009
All right, take your drill-bit money
and put it in the bank.


85
00:07:04.176 --> 00:07:06.845
If you continue making
the movie the way you are ...


86
00:07:07.013 --> 00:07:09.306
... there isn't gonna be a distributor ...

87
00:07:09.473 --> 00:07:12.434
