any more oil money.


89
00:07:15.438 --> 00:07:18.481
So welcome to Hollywood.

90
00:07:18.649 --> 00:07:22.027
Yeah. Well, I'll be sure
to remember that, Mr. Mayer.


91
00:07:22.194 --> 00:07:24.029
- Good luck.
- All right.


92
00:07:24.196 --> 00:07:27.365
He needs 26 to make it work?
