Then we'll wait.

202
00:13:40.072 --> 00:13:42.407
Look, whatever they pay
you at UCLA ...


203
00:13:42.574 --> 00:13:46.202
... I'm doubling it, all right?
You work for me now. Find some clouds.


204
00:13:47.663 --> 00:13:49.038
Find some clouds.

205
00:13:49.707 --> 00:13:51.457
Find me some clouds!

206
00:13:51.625 --> 00:13:53.835
Welcome to Hell's Angels.

207
00:13:57.047 --> 00:13:58.256
Thank you.

208
00:14:06.932 --> 00:14:10.393
I've been to Chatsworth,
Santa Cruz, Encino, San Diego ...


209
00:14:10.561 --> 00:14:14.439
