It has been eight months!


210
00:14:14.606 --> 00:14:16.399
Where are my goddamn clouds, huh?

211
00:14:16.567 --> 00:14:18.901
They move, Mr. Hughes!

212
00:14:19.069 --> 00:14:20.403
Clouds move.

213
00:14:20.571 --> 00:14:23.031
