253
00:17:38.060 --> 00:17:40.019
Yes.
We're gonna move up in the Bronx.


254
00:17:40.187 --> 00:17:42.271
Green grass,
a lot of people you know.


255
00:17:42.439 --> 00:17:45.149
The Ginsbergs,
the Guttenbergs and the Goldbergs.


256
00:17:45.317 --> 00:17:47.985
Oh, a whole lot of "bergs."
I don't know them all.


257
00:17:48.612 --> 00:17:52.365
See, this is what the people want.
Silent pictures are yesterday's news.


258
00:17:52.532 --> 00:17:55.534
So I figure we gotta re-shoot
Hell's Angels for sound.


259
00:17:57.955 --> 00:17:59.497
How much of it?

260
00:17:59.665 --> 00:18:01.916
All of it.
Before you ask, I'll tell you.


261
00:18:02.084 --> 00:18:04.961
An additional 1.7 million.
We got that much?


262
00:18:06.088 --> 00:18:09.340
- No!
- Well, we'll make it.


263
00:18:09.508 --> 00:18:11.259
Take care of that, would you?

264
00:18:11.426 --> 00:18:12.760
Now, get this.

265
00:18:22.854 --> 00:18:25.022
In the halls of 7000 Romaine ...

266
00:18:25.190 --> 00:18:27.608
... it goes on day after day,
month after month.


267
00:18:27.776 --> 00:18:31.487
Howard Hughes is now editing
some 25 miles of film.


268
00:18:32.864 --> 00:18:37.493
Heck, I say release it now and give
the world its first 560-hour movie.


269
00:18:37.661 --> 00:18:41.914
