278
00:19:25.500 --> 00:19:29.337
And tell Jimmy I want

279
00:19:29.504 --> 00:19:32.381
Medium chips,
none too close to the outside.


280
00:19:32.549 --> 00:19:34.050
Got it?

281
00:19:34.217 --> 00:19:36.552
You remember
that goddamn shot from reel 10?


282
00:19:36.720 --> 00:19:39.305
No. I don't remember
anything from reel 10.


283
00:19:39.473 --> 00:19:41.640
