1203
01:35:09.957 --> 01:35:12.584
- Oh, my God!
- Goddamn it!


1204
01:35:14.211 --> 01:35:15.461
Faith!

1205
01:35:16.255 --> 01:35:18.172
- Faith, what the hell?
- Look out!


1206
01:35:18.340 --> 01:35:21.050
Goddamn, what the hell are you doing?

1207
01:35:24.221 --> 01:35:26.973
