- What are you doing with her?


1208
01:35:27.141 --> 01:35:29.809
We are going to dinner.
Now, get out of there.


1209
01:35:29.977 --> 01:35:31.978
Get that crazy bitch away from me!

1210
01:35:32.146 --> 01:35:33.771
Don't you love me anymore?

1211
01:35:33.939 --> 01:35:35.481
Course I love you, pork chop.

1212
01:35:35.649 --> 01:35:37.442
Ava, look over here. Howard.

1213
01:35:38.152 --> 01:35:39.444
