1328
01:44:51.538 --> 01:44:55.624
Oh, Christ, I don't know, Beverly Hills.
Fifteen hundred feet.


1329
01:44:55.792 --> 01:44:57.501
We're going down.

1330
01:44:58.420 --> 01:45:02.047
I'll try for the Wilshire Country Club.
Ninth hole. You reading me?


1331
01:45:02.215 --> 01:45:06.135
Wilshire Country Club, copy that.
Howard, reduce engines to 1,000.


1332
01:45:06.845 --> 01:45:11.807
I'm going down!
I'm not gonna make it, buddy!


1333
01:45:18.273 --> 01:45:20.065
Goddamn it!

