1347
01:48:18.703 --> 01:48:20.245
From our stock.

1348
01:48:20.914 --> 01:48:25.084
- Oh, he's not going to like that.
- Mr. Dietrich, I doubt he's ...


1349
01:48:25.251 --> 01:48:28.212
... ever gonna like or
dislike anything again.


1350
01:48:28.838 --> 01:48:31.006
I'm terribly sorry.

1351
01:48:59.452 --> 01:49:01.370
Orange juice.

1352
01:49:04.457 --> 01:49:07.918
It's not fresh from
the kitchen, so I ...

1353
01:49:08.628 --> 01:49:13.716
I have them make it here so ...
So I can see.


1354
01:49:17.804 --> 01:49:19.763
Look at me.

1355
01:49:22.392 --> 01:49:24.393
I'm a monster.

1356
