They ... They attract aphids.

1386
01:51:45.910 --> 01:51:50.622
Aphids are ...
They're just awful little creatures.


1387
01:51:51.457 --> 01:51:53.250
But ...

1388
01:51:55.587 --> 01:51:57.671
